POST-INSTALL:

		* Recompile gcc with option --enable-languages=c,c++,objc,f77,ada 
		  or use the gcc port in this repository

		* Set this environment variables in your ~/.bashrc:
		export PGPLOT_DIR=/usr/lib/pgplot
		export PGPLOT_FONT=/usr/lib/pgplot/grfont.dat
		export PGPLOT_RGB=/usr/lib/pgplot/rgb.txt

